{"word":"G277 - ἀμετακίνητος - ametakínētos - am-et-ak-in'-ay-tos - Unmovable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀμετακίνητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ametakínētos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">am-et-ak-in'-ay-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unmovable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அசையாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"not to be moved from its place, unmoved, firmly persistent"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3334 - μετακινέω - metakinéō - met-ak-ee-neh'-o/3334\">G3334</a>; <i>immovable:</i> - unmovable.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}